Q: 查询所有在17th Of September起降的航班，并找出最常用的飞机型号。
SQL:
SELECT b.aircraft_model_name, count(*) AS num
FROM zts_plane_flight a LEFT JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE ( a.dep_icao = "FNBG" OR a.arr_icao = "FNBG" ) AND b.aircraft_model_name IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY b.aircraft_model_name
ORDER BY num DESC LIMIT 3;
